# Assets Management Guide

Static assets handling:

- Favicon configuration:
  - Place favicon.ico directly in the public directory
  - No route handler needed for favicon.ico
  - Cache control headers configured in [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js)

- Image optimization:
  - Use Next.js Image component for external images
  - Configure remote patterns in [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js)
  - Local images should be placed in the public directory

- Icons:
  - Using @heroicons/react for consistent icon set
  - Import from @heroicons/react/24/outline for outlined style
  - Import from @heroicons/react/24/solid for filled style
